For fruit salad: Pour 1 1/4 cups water into a medium saucepan. Add SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend and bring to a boil, stirring occasionally. Remove from heat and let cool. Pour into a large mixing bowl and stir in Kirsch, lemon juice, and vanilla. Add apples, cantaloupe, honeydew, grapes, plums or peaches, oranges, and blueberries to the bowl. Gently combine until well coated. Cover and refrigerate at least 1 hour or up to 3 days. For yogurt sauce: Combine yogurt, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and pumpkin pie spice, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, dissolves. Just before serving, gently fold raspberries and strawberries into fruit salad. Divide among 6 bowls and top each with yogurt sauce.